        <num>44-3-179</num>
        <content>
          <p>The developer shall immediately amend or supplement the public offering statement to report any material change in the information required by Code Section 44-3-172. As to any exchange program, the developer shall use the current written materials that are supplied to it for distribution to the time-share interval owners as it is received.</p>
